  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this observational study is to evaluate the quality of life in patients with
      congenital afibrinogenemia using the Haemo-QoL SF for kids and the Haem-A-QoL for adult
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this observational study, children and adults suffering from congenital afibrinogenemia
      confirmed by biology will be enrolled. All patients will receive a questionnaire on quality
      of life in their own language during a routine visit and filled out by the patient at home. A
      general questionnaire will be filled out by the patient's physician.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
